ies to `done` in both sprint-state.json and sprint-status.yaml, updated sprint totals (70->74).\n- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph stale in-memory state overwrites. 54th occurrence.\n- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n- **CRITICAL**: Ralph must be stopped. 54 consecutive no-op sessions wasting tokens on the same fix.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: ~14\n- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 5, Edit: 6, Grep: 0, Write: 1, Glob: 2\n- Files read: 3 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None — known recurring issue efficiently fixed\n","numLines":17,"startLine":1,"totalLines":17}}}
